<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 yǒu fú tóng xiǎng yǒu nán tóng dāng, dì xiōng xiāng ài jiù shì lì liàng.
 niǎo ér xiàng wǎng tiān kōng yú ér xiàng wǎng hǎi yáng, shén de ér nǚ xiàng wǎng jiā hé mù guó xìng wàng.
 hé yī yǒng yuǎn bù néng wàng. xiāng ài cháng jì zài xīn shàng.
 yǐ qiān bēi shù yāo, xīn xiōng yào kuān guǎng. yīn wèi shén de hào tǒng kuài chuī xiǎng.</lyrics>
<title>yǒu fú tóng xiǎng yǒu nán tóng dāng 迦南840</title>
<hymn_number>840</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>